22:07.993 --> 22:09.824
(tires squeal )

22:13.082 --> 22:15.038
( radio chatter)

22:21.382 --> 22:23.668
He's in.
You can start packing.

22:27.721 --> 22:29.507
Soldier, can you hear me?

22:31.559 --> 22:33.424
