22:33.602 --> 22:35.513
Cyanosis.
Chest contusion.

22:35.688 --> 22:37.019
What are we
looking at here?

22:37.189 --> 22:38.599
Collapsed lung.

22:38.774 --> 22:40.856
Very good.
Tube him.

22:43.737 --> 22:46.524
