The outer layers
have less nerves.

26:02.644 --> 26:06.478
The deeper,
the more sensitive.

26:08.984 --> 26:11.145
You need a steady hand.

26:15.491 --> 26:18.233
- What is Cobalt?
- I don't know.

26:19.995 --> 26:21.656
