28:38.467 --> 28:39.957
- Nick: I'm not sick.
- Soldier: Here we go.

28:40.135 --> 28:41.966
Yeah, and I'm not giving it back.

28:42.137 --> 28:43.593
Of course not.
A deal's a deal.

28:43.764 --> 28:45.629
But I'm suggesting
an additional transaction.

28:45.807 --> 28:48.219
Something to round out
the ensemble.

28:48.393 --> 28:51.430
Nick: I'm not sick.
I swear, I swear.

28:51.605 --> 28:52.936
Hold.

28:53.106 --> 28:54.642
Easy.

28:54.816 --> 28:57.432
Let me have the boy.
