29:40.654 --> 29:42.190
Who's A?

29:43.198 --> 29:44.984
( radio chatter)

29:46.702 --> 29:49.660
( gate buzzes )

29:49.830 --> 29:51.866
Man: Hey, man,
where y'all going to?

29:54.710 --> 29:56.996
Clear, clear!

29:58.880 --> 30:00.541
(snarling )

30:00.716 --> 30:02.877
Here we go,
here we go.

30:07.014 --> 30:08.129
(gunfire)

30:08.307 --> 30:10.343
- Wait, where's Moyers?
- He got held up.

30:10.517 --> 30:12.223
What happened?

30:12.394 --> 30:14.476
He ain't coming.

30:16.815 --> 30:19.557
We'll get you within a few blocks.
Walk home from there.

30:19.735 --> 30:22.397
But Moyers said he'd take me
to the command post, the doctor.

30:22.571 --> 30:24.402
We're not going
near that place, man.

30:24.573 --> 30:26.905
I got a new mission-- operation
get my ass back to San Diego.

30:27.075 --> 30:28.235
( pounding )
Let's go.

30:28.410 --> 30:30.366
(tires squealing )

30:32.372 --> 30:34.658
( Ofelia screaming )

30:40.213 --> 30:42.249
Ofelia.
What--?

30:44.176 --> 30:46.417
Wait, what?
What? Wait.

31:10.035 --> 31:12.117
She was nine years old

31:12.287 --> 31:14.699
when she first asked me
about the war

31:14.873 --> 31:17.364
and why we came to America.

31:18.960 --> 31:21.292
And I told her

31:21.463 --> 31:24.125
in detail

31:24.299 --> 31:27.462
about the violence,

31:27.636 --> 31:29.718
what was done,

31:29.888 --> 31:31.424
how we suffered.

31:31.598 --> 31:33.759
(water running)

31:33.934 --> 31:35.799
I told her everything

31:35.977 --> 31:40.471
except which man
was me.

31:47.155 --> 31:49.942
(voice breaks )
