31:52.411 --> 31:54.948
that it was necessary then...

31:56.456 --> 31:57.992
to survive?

32:01.586 --> 32:04.999
That it is necessary again?

32:28.029 --> 32:30.111
Did he tell us
what we need to know?

32:47.340 --> 32:50.207
( people chattering, crying )

33:00.812 --> 33:03.224
(monitor beeping )

