34:11.591 --> 34:13.798
These are real people.

34:15.262 --> 34:17.628
Built a whole life here.

34:24.312 --> 34:26.769
(sighs)

34:26.940 --> 34:28.771
And now...

34:33.989 --> 34:35.980
( glass shatters )

35:20.285 --> 35:22.276
Ofelia.

35:28.668 --> 35:30.374
Ofelia?

35:34.007 --> 35:36.214
- ( door opens, closes)
- Maddy. Maddy.

35:36.384 --> 35:38.124
Thank God you're okay.

35:41.348 --> 35:43.714
Did you know
what he was gonna do?

35:47.354 --> 35:49.310
You didn't know?

35:50.815 --> 35:53.067
Tell me you didn't know.

35:55.862 --> 35:57.318
Adams: That's when
the screaming started.

35:57.489 --> 35:59.980
It happened so fast.

36:00.158 --> 36:02.820
I'd never seen them
turn that fast before.

36:02.994 --> 36:06.077
All those people,
2,000 of them, just...

36:09.250 --> 36:11.502
trampling each other.

36:11.670 --> 36:14.377
And they couldn't--

36:15.674 --> 36:18.916
they couldn't get out and...

36:19.094 --> 36:22.257
(sighs ) we couldn't tell
the infected from--

36:23.848 --> 36:25.713
oh, God.

36:27.686 --> 36:29.768
I can hear them.

36:32.273 --> 36:34.730
I can still hear them.

36:34.901 --> 36:37.563
- Yeah...
- What did you do?

36:37.737 --> 36:40.570
We locked them in the arena.

36:40.740 --> 36:42.605
l chained the doors.

36:43.785 --> 36:45.616
That's what I did.

36:45.787 --> 36:47.573
I believe you.

