37:28.455 --> 37:30.821
Our people.
Tell him.

37:30.999 --> 37:32.489
Tell him what
happens to them.

37:32.667 --> 37:35.750
Cobalt includes procedures

37:35.920 --> 37:39.663
for the humane
termination of...

37:42.260 --> 37:44.342
(sighs)

37:49.184 --> 37:51.345
When?

37:51.519 --> 37:53.635
0900 tomorrow.

