38:36.523 --> 38:38.184
There's a difference.

38:40.735 --> 38:42.566
The game has changed.

38:42.737 --> 38:45.069
We return to the old rules.

38:47.742 --> 38:50.074
And the people

38:50.245 --> 38:52.031
who won the last round

38:52.205 --> 38:54.070
with their grande lattes

38:54.249 --> 38:56.706
and their frequent flyer miles

